TE Compatible Wire Assembly

Custom TE-compatible wire assemblies manufactured to your specifications. Support for Econoseal, AMP MCP, AMPSEAL, Superseal, and MATE-N-LOK series with pitch range 1.5mm to 4.14mm. UL-certified wire, 100% electrical testing, and ISO-compliant quality control.

Disclaimer: These are TE-compatible connector cable assemblies manufactured by Trycay. We are not affiliated with TE Connectivity. All assemblies are produced to meet TE series specifications and are fully compatible with TE connectors.
